    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 368240.0,
      "end_time": 371620.0,
      "text": "and local militia to protect the world from devastation"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 371640.0,
      "end_time": 374880.0,
      "text": "But Taiwan paid a high price for this so-called “peace”"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 374880.0,
      "end_time": 377440.0,
      "text": "Taiwanese people lived under police surveillance"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 377440.0,
      "end_time": 379640.0,
      "text": "Common folks had to call the police “Sir”"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 379640.0,
      "end_time": 381400.0,
      "text": "Parents threatened their kids by saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 381400.0,
      "end_time": 382460.0,
      "text": "“The cops are coming!”"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 382480.0,
      "end_time": 383860.0,
      "text": "And just by seeing the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 383860.0,
      "end_time": 385380.0,
      "text": "Everyone wet their pants"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 385380.0,
      "end_time": 388300.0,
      "text": "Later on, Goto proclaimed the Bandit Punishment Ordinance"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 388300.0,
      "end_time": 390300.0,
      "text": "giving the police even greater power"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 390560.0,
      "end_time": 393100.0,
      "text": "More than 5900 people were arrested"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 393100.0,
      "end_time": 395720.0,
      "text": "and more than 3200 of them were executed"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 395720.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "You can probably guess that Taiwanese people were"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400240.0,
      "text": "pretty well behaved after that"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 401780.0,
      "end_time": 404640.0,
      "text": "Now, you probably understand a little bit more about how Kudo"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 406480.0,
      "end_time": 409800.0,
      "text": "How Goto Shinpei prevented Taiwan from being sold to France"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 409800.0,
      "end_time": 411800.0,
      "text": "To sell or not to sell"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 411800.0,
      "end_time": 415200.0,
      "text": "Japan weighed its options rationally from a colonial perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 415200.0,
      "end_time": 417000.0,
      "text": "but also with a romantic touch"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 417000.0,
      "end_time": 419060.0,
      "text": "to prove itself to Western countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 419060.0,
      "end_time": 419540.0,
      "text": "Anyhow"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 419540.0,
      "end_time": 421740.0,
      "text": "When we look back at specific parts of history"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 421740.0,
      "end_time": 424020.0,
      "text": "Avoiding emotional judgments is really important"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 424020.0,
      "end_time": 425740.0,
      "text": "for us to get closer to the truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 425740.0,
      "end_time": 427540.0,
      "text": "If Taiwan was actually sold to France"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 427540.0,
      "end_time": 428980.0,
      "text": "What would our lives be like now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 428980.0,
      "end_time": 431500.0,
      "text": "If you still think that’s an easy question to answer..."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 431500.0,
      "end_time": 433120.0,
      "text": "Well, we just wasted 7 minutes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 433120.0,
      "end_time": 433540.0,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 433540.0,
      "end_time": 435760.0,
      "text": "After all that talking, I’m a bit thirsty"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 435760.0,
      "end_time": 436920.0,
      "text": "Let me drink this sake"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 436920.0,
      "end_time": 438560.0,
      "text": "And we’ll see you next time"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 438560.0,
      "end_time": 439320.0,
      "text": "Bye!"
    }
  ]
}